<div dir="ltr"><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">Hi Folks!!</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"> </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">
We announced a bug fix release of Ushahidi, dubbed <a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/Ushahidi_Web/releases/tag/2.7.4">v2.7.4</a> last evening. We knocked out a couple of bugs and improvements such as:</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">
</p><ul style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"><li style="margin-left:15px">Password validation errors<br></li><li style="margin-left:15px">Runtime errors in settings and when submitting reports<br>
</li><li style="margin-left:15px">Updating Openlayers to v2.13.1<br></li><li style="margin-left:15px">Addition of missing files during a fresh install</li></ul><p style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">
</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">For a full run down of all the fixed bugs and improvements, have a look at the <a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/Ushahidi_Web/issues?q=milestone%3Av2.7.4+is%3Aclosed" target="_blank">2.7.4 milestone on our github issues page</a>.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">Crowdmap Classic should be updated to match this release by 6<sup>th</sup> August, 2014. Communication on this will be made once the update is complete</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"> </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">A list of all plugins compatible with this version can be found on <a href="mailto:https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Plugin+Version+Compatibility" target="_blank">our plugins compatibility wiki page</a>.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"> </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"><b>Thank </b><b>you!</b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">
 </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">As always, this release happened with the help of our greater community. Huge thanks to all of you who sent in those bug reports, pull requests, translations, questions and comments. These went a long way in making this release happen.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:15pt;font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"><span style="color:black">Even as we move forward with development on v3, we definitely encourage you to keep sending in those pull requests and sending in your translation contributions on v2!!</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"><b><span style="color:black">Looking towards v3!</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:15pt;font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">
<span style="color:black">We’re getting closer and closer to launching the new version of Ushahidi(v3), and want to make sure that what we envision matches what you envision from the revamped platform.</span></p><ul type="disc" style="font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><b><a href="https://drive.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/?ddrp=1#folders/0B5redy59hE0qbzRqNjRMYjF2RTQ" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Community Paths</span></a></b>: We want to better understand how to meet your goals and expectations on v3 based on your experience with Ushahidi v2. We want to know how the tools helps or hinders you from achieving your deployment goals. Take a few minutes of your time this week and share your experiences with us. <a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1kNWUXVfJs8KGj0LSbIGZ9UiC_Wr8PFlXJsnHJ2Lm4N0/edit#heading=h.koyyn2qxwob1" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Instructions here</span></a></li>
<ul type="circle"><li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1IbIE2c_08t1j_PWg32A05lkPAo7AWY59R40Cgcdqf98/edit#heading=h.n9fhyp2b7g3" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Disaster response</span></a></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1Frd2RveoCBJR_G0uwlt9wpKXigg1RhF5PeqqxoX3J2M/edit" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Human Rights Mapping</span></a></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1sD5b-DZUgCMhVCensP26XjvG1hGwT2s3YlbHgUHL-PM/edit" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Anti-Corruption Mapping</span></a></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1LWk_rlVrihlerXRovfXusaoXtHFpLVfJSga5CQJkKiQ/edit" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Election Monitoring</span></a></li>
<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/180qknWEoSxJcSrRBHlCqxYp91EN-Nzfaq6M6ENsHjCM/edit" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Environmental Mapping</span></a></li>
</ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:15px;color:black"><b>Feature requests</b>: Are there any features you feel we should be prioritising that are not on <a href="https://phabricator.ushahidi.com/project/board/1/" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">the roadmap</span></a>? Are there any features on v2.x that you feel could be handled better with v3? <a href="https://phabricator.ushahidi.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Log this on Phabricator</span></a>( <a href="https://phabricator.ushahidi.com/w/help/phabricator/" target="_blank"><span style="color:rgb(89,143,201);text-decoration:none">Here’s a guide to get you started</span></a> ).</li>
</ul><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:15pt;font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.333333969116211px"><span style="color:black">Incase you have any questions on this, feel free to reach out to me.</span></p></div>
